data.description: Spacious Country Living Priced Right in the Highly Rated Northwest ISD!  This Lovely Home sits on just over ONE ACRE & has NEW flooring Throughout, NEW Interior Paint, NEW Blinds, NEW Paint on All Cabinets, NEW Lighting Fixtures, NEW Granite Countertops, & More. Loads of Natural Light Pouring into this 4 Bedroom, 2 & a Half Bathroom Home. The Second Living Area can be an Office Space, Game Room, Etc.  A Wood Burning Fireplace in the Main Living Room Keeps the Family Cozy all Winter Long. The Primary Bedroom is Downstairs with an EnSuite Primary Bathroom that has Dual Separate Vanities, Stand Up Shower & Large Walk-In Closet. Enjoy Over an Acre of Fenced Space! Build Your Dream Shop, Pool, Playground, Garden - There's Room for it All!  Bring Your Horses & Chickens!  No HOA & Outside of the City Limits gives More Flexibility for Making This Your Dream Home!   Buyer & Agent to Verify All Info Within This Listing Including Square Footage, Schools, Services, Easements, Tax, Etc.
